ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectOrder Repealing Orders in Council P.C. 2013-175 and P.C. 1992-706
PrecisOrder repealing Orders in Council P.C. 1992-706 of April 9, 1992 and P.C. 2013-175 of February 28, 2013 in order to allow the Minister of Crown-Indigenous Relations to execute specific claim settlement agreements that do not require land regularization pursuant to the Indian Act.
